name: Gooey guy
bio: Hi, this is my bio. I'm just a lyrical genuis looking for some guys who can match my flow putting out beats in the dorms. My favorite show is stranger things, and I like to just chill on a friday night with a boba tea and some pop tarts. Really living the life out here. You should match me if you're another cool gemini with a fire pair of Yeezys and a touch of swag. This year is gonna be lit, Ye out.
